<div id="home-page">
  <div class="plank secondary-md main-feature under-logo">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-sm-12">
          <%= large_modal('intro-video',
               title: '',
               content: '<div style="text-align: center">
                          <iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/99267372" width="800" height="450" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> 
                        </div>'
          ) %>
          <div class="video-quote">
            <p class="shoutout">ARE WE MISSING OUT ON EXTRAORDINARY TALENT?</p>
            <p class="feature">
              While athletic talent scouting starts at early ages and is robust, there is no comparable system for scouting young academic and leadership talent. Beyond Z is here to change that.
            </p>
          </div>
          <i data-toggle="modal" data-target="#intro-video" class="intro-play-button"></i>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="plank primary-lt">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3 text-center">
          <p>
            The Beyond Z career accelerator discovers, develops, and connects diverse talent to networks and opportunities they deserve.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center">
          <p class="shoutout">
            We believe our next generation of global leaders can emerge from everywhere.
          </p>
          <%= join_us_button_large %>
          <br />
          <br />
          <strong>More info:</strong><br />
          <%= light_page_jump 'For Students', 'for-students' %> |
          <%= light_page_jump 'For Volunteers', 'for-volunteers' %> |
          <%= light_page_jump 'For Partners', 'for-partners' %>
          <br />
          <br />
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="plank plain-md">
    <div class="section-container text-center">
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <h2>
            Our Approach
          </h2>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="infographic-column">
          <div class="discover-icon"></div>
          <h3>Discover</h3>
          <p>young people with the focus, drive, and talent to be great</p>
        </div>
        <div class="infographic-column">
          <div class="develop-icon"></div>
          <h3>Develop</h3>
          <p>their authentic leadership and 21st century career skills</p>
        </div>
        <div class="infographic-column">
          <div class="connect-icon"></div>
          <h3>Connect</h3>
          <p>them to inspiring students, influential advocates, and career opportunities</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a id="for-students"></a>
  <div class="plank plain-lt">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-lg-4 no-pad for-students">
          <%= image_tag 'for_students.jpg' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <h2>
            For K-12 and College Students
          </h2>
          <blockquote>
            <p>"Beyond Z introduced me into the real world outside of academics! My interviewing and networking skills have definitely grown - I have met some incredible people and stayed in touch with many of them. My decision to enter the Education field has been reinforced through my time at BZ as well!"
            </p>
            <footer>Martha Mendoza<br />University of California at Berkeley, 2016</footer>
          </blockquote>
          <%= learn_more_link 'applying as a student', apply_path %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a id="for-volunteers"></a>
  <div class="plank plain-md">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
         <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-push-8 no-pad for-volunteers">
          <%= image_tag 'for_volunteers.jpg' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-pull-4">
          <h2>
            For Volunteers
          </h2>
          <blockquote>
            <p>"I loved getting to know the kids and hanging out with them - we got to know each of their personalities really well. I particularly loved watching them plan the Hackathon and seeing their efforts pay off. Their excitement for coding, planning, and leading at Beyond Hacks was contagious and I was thrilled for them."
            </p>
            <footer>Aly Mejia<br />Leadership Coach</footer>
          </blockquote>
          <%= learn_more_link 'volunteering', volunteer_path %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a id="for-partners"></a>
  <div class="plank plain-lt">
    <div class="section-container">
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
          <h2>
            For Partners
          </h2>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <blockquote>
            <p>"Beyond Z's mission is so important â€“ provide leadership development to young people, especially first-generation college students, so that they are positioned to excel at the highest level and become global leaders.</p>
            <p>I hire Beyond Z interns because they are exceptionally talented. They are smart, passionate, and driven college students who get results."</p>
            <footer>Patrick O'Donnell<br />Vice President of Parent and Family Engagement, Teach For America</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <blockquote>
            <p>"All young people should be able to dream without boundaries. I am excited to be an inaugural partner with Beyond Z because their curriculum and programming will help to level the playing field for under-represented populations lacking resources and human capital necessary to reach the highest levels of leadership."</p>
            <footer>Kaya Henderson<br />Chancellor, Washington D.C. Public Schools</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
          <%= learn_more_link 'partnering with us', partner_path %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="plank primary-lt">
    <div class="section-container text-center">
      <section>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <p class="shoutout">Ready to jumpstart your leadership path today?</p>
          <br />
          <%= join_us_button %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
